    year: '2023',
    title: 'Modular Quantum Interconnects (IBM System Two)',
    description: 'IBM designs System Two, a massive dry dilution architecture bridging multiple fridge units. <strong>Contribution:</strong> Broke the volumetric and cooling-power bottleneck of single cryostats. Allows scaling beyond 1,000 physical qubits by sharing cryogenic vacuum boundaries and distributing the massive heat load of thousands of RF coaxial cables.'
  }
